Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-helloworld layer to your build
 II. Compile Source Code
III. Install Binary file


I. Adding the meta-helloworld layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-helloworld'

II. Compile Source Code
========

Run 'bitbake helloworld' to build example code
Run 'bitbake -c clean helloworld' to clean example code

III. Install Binary file
========

Add IMAGE_INSTALL_append += " helloworld" in /{poky root dir}/build/conf/local.conf
IMAGE_INSTALL detail description, please check https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/3.1/ref-manual/ref-manual.html#var-IMAGE_INSTALL
